subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Petra Kvitova swept aside Caroline Garcia, 6-3, 6-4, to reach the semifinals of the Wuhan Open, while Caroline Wozniacki rallied to beat Timea Bacsinszky, 4-6, 6-2, 6-3.
